    Yakitori (Kushiyaki)
    Yakitori () are grilled chicken skewers made from bite sized pieces of meat from all different parts of the chicken, such as the breasts, thighs, skin, liver and other innards. However, here at Shokudo Yakitori or Kushiyaki are anything we skewered. We prepare to perfection and cooked over ceramic briquettes gas grill, yakitori is a popular, inexpensive dish commonly enjoyed together with a glass of beer.
